In accounting, these items are typically classified as "Fixed Assets" or "Property, Plant and Equipment (PP&E)". These are tangible, long-term assets used in business operations.

Looking at the balance sheet provided, I can see the line item "Fixed Assets" which represents:
- Initial value: 8000000.00 (as of 2023-12-31)
- End value: 9213417.20 (as of 2024-02-02)

This is exactly what the task is asking for - the tangible items held for business operations.
